<title>USA: Ceridian agrees to acquire FLX.</title>
<headline>Ceridian agrees to acquire FLX.</headline>
<dateline>MINNEAPOLIS 1997-02-20</dateline>
<text>
<p>Ceridian Corp said Thursday it agreed to acquire FLX Corp, a developer of human resources management and benefits software.</p>
<p>Terms were not disclosed. The transaction is expected to close within 30 days.</p>
<p>FLX, based in Malvern, Pa., had 1996 revenue of $3.7 million. It will retain its name and operate as an independent entity.</p>
<p>Ceridian is an information services and defense electronics company.</p>
<p>	 ((Chicago newsdesk 312 408-8787))</p>
